        "category": "ancestry",
        "description": {
            "value": "<p><strong>Requirements</strong> You're in quadrupedal posture.</p><hr /><p>You use the momentum from lifting yourself up into bipedal posture to propel yourself into a high leap. You @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.actions.Item.Change Posture] from quadrupedal to bipedal and [[/act high-jump]] or @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.actions.Item.Leap] with a +2 circumstance bonus to Athletics. You don't automatically fail if you don't Stride as part of the activity. You remain in bipedal posture when you land.</p><hr /><p><strong>Special</strong> If you have the @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.feats.Item.Quick Jump] skill feat, this activity is also reduced to 1 action.</p>"
        },
